## üì± Key UI Components to Design

### Navigation
- **Primary Menu**: Home, Services (dropdown with 8 items), About Us, Contact
- **Mobile Menu**: Hamburger with same hierarchy
- **Footer Menu**: Privacy Policy, Contact, About Us

### Forms
**Contact Form Fields**:
- Name (required)
- Email (required)
- Phone (required)
- Service Needed (dropdown with all 8 services + Other)
- Preferred Date (date picker)
- Message (text area)

### Interactive Elements
- **Buttons**: Primary (`#FF9500`), Secondary (white/outlined)
- **Cards**: White/light grey background, subtle border, hover lift effect
- **Accordions**: For FAQ sections
- **Pricing Tables**: Highlighted "recommended" tier option
- **Booking Widget**: Integration point for Amelia booking system

### Trust Badges/Icons
- ‚úì 100% Bond Back Guarantee
- ‚úì Fully Insured
- ‚úì Professional Team
- ‚úì Same Day Available

